body
  .container
    .jumbotron.text-center
      .logo
        a(href="https://sas.utmn.ru")
          img(src="/assets/logo_sas_ut_short-red.svg")
      h1 Feedback. 3rd quarter. History.
      h3 Please select 
      form(action="/polls/feedback-collector" method="post")
        input(type="hidden" value="history_corinne" name="subject")    
        fieldset
          div(class="input-group")
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously") To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously? Give a score from 1 to 10, where 1 = It did not help at all and 10 = It helped significantly.
              input(type="number" required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent was this course an improvement over English language courses you have had previously" min="1" max="10")
            .flex-container
              label(for="In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills") In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills? Put your thoughts. 
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="In what ways was this course useful in terms of improving your English language skills" rows="4")  
            .flex-container
              label(for="If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be?") If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be? Put your thoughts. 
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="If you had the chance to change some aspects of the course what would they be?" rows="4")  
            .flex-container
              label(for="Who taught this course (speaking)") Who was the instructor for this course (speaking)?
              select(class="form-control" required="required" name="Who taught this course (speaking)")
                option(value="Jeff Bain") Jeffery Bain
                option(value="Steven Kaye") Steven Kaye
            .flex-container
              label(for="Who taught this course (grammar)") Who was the instructor for this course (grammar)?
              select(class="form-control" required="required" name="Who taught this course (grammar)")
                option(value="I. Parakhina") Irina Parakhina
                option(value="Zh. Vasileva") Zhanna Vasileva
                option(value="E. Novokreshhennykh") Ekaterina Novokreshhennykh
                option(value="D. Glovatskaya") Diana Glovatskaya
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent did the instructor focus on speaking skills?") To what extent did the instructor focus on speaking skills? Put your thoughts. 
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent did the instructor focus on speaking skills?" rows="4")  
            .flex-container
              label(for="To what extent did the instructor focus on grammar skills?") To what extent did the instructor focus on grammar skills? Put your thoughts. 
              textarea(required="required" class="form-control" name="To what extent did the instructor focus on grammar skills?" rows="4")    
        button(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg") Submit
